  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2025-02-24",
    "date": "2025-05-02T19:36:24Z",
    "text": "Falun Gong Protection Act\n\nThis bill requires the President to impose visa- and property-blocking sanctions on foreign persons that have knowingly and directly engaged in or facilitated the involuntary harvesting of organs in China.\n\nSanctions may not be imposed on the importation of goods or with respect to specified transactions related to humanitarian assistance.\n\nThe authority to impose sanctions under this bill expires five years after enactment."
  },
